      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, im in dubai rn and just landed from a super long flight. my chest has been feeling really sharp and tight for the last hour and i can barely catch my breath. i think im just having a massive panic attack bc of the travel stress and the jet lag... is that normal or should i be worried?",
