      "content": "thanks. it does feel kind of like anxiety, i guess. like my heart is just racing and i feel super restless. i don't really want to go to a hospital in a foreign country if i don't have to, its so expensive and stressful. do u think i can just take some calming meds or maybe some extra melatonin to sleep it off and see if it's gone in the morning?",
